To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AbandonedBaby _abandonedbaby;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_abandonedbaby = AbandonedBaby(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_abandonedbaby.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "abandonedbaby", _abandonedbaby.Current.Value);
}
